Subject: My Top Ten (about) Things I Love about Owning a Bus (it is

10. It's shape (I love every one of those curves).
9.  Working on it (everything is fixable, and mostly by me).
8.  It's roominess, practicality, thriftiness, efficiency.
7.  I can work on the underneath stuff without a jack.
6.  I have never had to get out of it and walk (unwillingly).
5.  It makes people happy to see it.
4.  It makes people happy to ride in it.
3.  Other old VW owners are usually friendly.
2.  Nearly everyone has owned an old VW and wants to tell me about it.
1.  Driving it.
0.  There are many resources to help with problems, especially this list.



